wsl --list --online
wsl --install <distro name>
wsl --list
wsl --list --verbose

HOW TO SHUTDOWN ALL DISTROS?
   - wsl --shutdown

HOW TO SHUTDOWN A PARTICULAR DISTRO?
   - wsl --terminate <distro name>

HOW TO SET A DEFAULT DISTRO ON WSL?
   - wsl --set-default <distro name>

HOW TO CHECK STATUS OF WSL?
  - wsl --status

HOW TO REMOVE A DISTRO?
  - wsl --unregister <distro-name>

ACCESSING WINDOWS FILES FROM A DISTRO?
      cd /mnt/c

HOW TO ACCESS LINUX FILES FROM WINDOWS?
   - Being in linux distro
   - explorer.exe . (current file location)
